episodes.title: A Very Venture Halloween
episodes.plot: Halloween Special of The Venture Bros.

episodes.title: What Color Is Your Cleansuit?
episodes.plot: Dr. Venture hires an army of college interns to help with his ambitious new science project. Dean finds love among the new recruits, but class warfare and nuclear physics threaten to tear the Venture Compound apart. And if they don't, The Monarch will.

episodes.title: Venture Libre
episodes.plot: One of Dr. Venture's old inventions seems to have gotten a mind of its own, so General Manhowers sends him to Central America to fix it. The Ventures must all confront their own hearts of darkness if they're to survive what's waiting for them in the jungle.

episodes.title: Sphinx Rising
episodes.plot: Henchman 21's command of Team SPHINX is starting to rub the O.S.I. the wrong way, and his new recruits are rubbing them even wronger.

episodes.title: Spanakopita
episodes.plot: Every year, since he was a little boy, Dr. Venture flies to the tiny island of Spanikos for a week of fun in the Grecian sun.

episodes.title: O.S.I. Love You
episodes.plot: Brock and the O.S.I. come under fire from the higher ups when they lose two high value super-criminal prisoners.

episodes.title: Momma's Boys
episodes.plot: A friendship built on lies threatens to unravel Dr. Venture's sanity.

episodes.title: Bot Seeks Bot
episodes.plot: Brock and the O.S.I. launch a bold and bizarre surveillance mission against one of the Council of 13's top members.

episodes.title: The Devil's Grip
episodes.plot: Dr. Venture is missing... presumed dead.
